					description = <"The design characteristics of the tip of the device that may affect insertion, positioning, or function.">
					comment = <"For example: rounded, beveled, Tiemann, Murphy eye, weighted, pigtail, coudé, fenestrated, step-tip, split-tip. Coding with a terminology system is preferred where possible.">
